            <title>[LU-12147] statone utility doesn&apos;t  form correct string with gcc8</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12147</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description></description>
                <environment>the following code:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;strncpy(parent, base, t - base);&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;offset = t - base - 1;&lt;br/&gt;
leaves parent with no terminating null with gcc8&lt;br/&gt;
and this breaks tests like recovery-small&lt;br/&gt;
</environment>
